Author: fishonthesun
Text: If they are pictures of a fond memory that you happen to be skinny in you should send them to someone who was also there so they arent lost forever and if you become more mentally recovered you can still have photos of the memory. If they are selfies or especially past body checks you should definitely delete them- it would be very beneficial for your recovery

Author: wrinkle-crease
Text: hide those pics, or get rid of them! and just keep making good progress with your health, working to improve your deficiencies and your ability to feel normal about eating. you can do it!! one day at a time. your life is worth it <3
